Qualifiers.Scope: Protection of tree roots during excavation

Variables.Dimensional: Tree root system extends beyond drip line, within first 18” below grade

Constants.Standards: Consult the city’s Tree Technical Manual
Constants.Procedures: Provide evidence of no harm to trees before building permit issuance

Conditions.Mandatory: Plan excavation to avoid harm to tree roots
Conditions.Conditional logic: Evidence required prior to building permit issuance

Relationships.Hierarchical: Tree protection is part of excavation planning
Relationships.Logical dependencies: Evidence of no harm required for permit
